# requires: if then
# Regression: literal-fold peephole must not rewind across a resolved branch
# target.  Before OPT_FENCE, `: th if 5 then + ;` compiled correctly on the
# true-flag path but crashed on the false-flag path because fold_plus_comp
# rewound HERE back into the bytes the `then` patch had already resolved.
: th  if 5 then + ;
7 1 -1 th .
7 1  0 th .
: td  if dup then + ;
1 2 -1 td .
1 2  0 td .
bye
